1. To build Orion Viewer from command line you will 
    need android-sdk-r21 and apache-ant 1.8 installed on your system.
2. Change path to android-sdk in orion_viewer/local.properties.
    See orion_viewer/local.properties.sample for example.
3. If you make build NOT for Highscreen/Spring Design Alex comment AlexDevice class
    in orion_viewer/src/universe/constellation/orion/viewer/device/
4. Go to orion_viewer folder (there is ant script: build.xml)
    and run 'ant' commmand with 'release' target:
	ant release

For Highscreen Alex:
3.b Select alex target in orion_viewer/project.properties
    or specify property alex.sdk.path in ant.properties
4.b Run command:
    ant -f build_alex.xml release

5. Project building will starts!